Getting started:
- download the brickd from tinkerforge:
  - Linux  http://download.tinkerforge.com/tools/brickd/linux/brickd-1.0.11_all.deb
  - Mac    http://download.tinkerforge.com/tools/brickd/macos/brickd_macos_1_0_11.dmg
  (see here http://www.tinkerforge.com/doc/Downloads.html#downloads-tools)
- install with dpkg -i ***.deb
- compile the code in this folder
- run
